{"members":[{"header_text":" فِقْهُ <teller> اَلرِّضَا، عَلَيْهِ السَّلاَمُ</teller> : ","body_text":"وَ مَنْ قَتَلَ مُؤْمِناً خَطَاً فَعَلَيْهِ عِتْقُ [رَقَبَةٍ] مُؤْمِنَةٍ اَوْ <quranic_text>«فَصِيٰامُ شَهْرَيْنِ مُتَتٰابِعَيْنِ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[المجادلة۴]</footnote> اَوْ <quranic_text>«فَاِطْعٰامُ سِتِّينَ مِسْكِيناً»</quranic_text> <footnote>[المجادلة۴]</footnote> وَ دِيَةٌ <quranic_text>«مُسَلَّمَةٌ اِليٰ اَهْلِهِ»</quranic_text> <footnote>[النساء۹۲]</footnote> .","translation":"","aligned_body":"وَ مَنْ قَتَلَ مُؤْمِناً خَطَاً فَعَلَيْهِ عِتْقُ رَقَبَةٍ مُؤْمِنَةٍ اَوْ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text فَصِيٰامُ شَهْرَيْنِ مُتَتٰابِعَيْنِ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote المجادلة ۴ TAG_CLOSE:footnote اَوْ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text فَاِطْعٰامُ سِتِّينَ مِسْكِيناً TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote المجادلة ۴ TAG_CLOSE:footnote وَ دِيَةٌ TAG_OPEN:quranic_text مُسَلَّمَةٌ اِليٰ اَهْلِهِ TAG_CLOSE:quranic_text TAG_OPEN:footnote النساء ۹۲ TAG_CLOSE:footnote"}],"body_consensus_columns":[{"kind":"word","token":"و","display":"وَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"من","display":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"word","token":"قتل","display":"قَتَلَ"},{"kind":"word","token":"مؤمنا","display":"مُؤْمِناً"},{"kind":"word","token":"خطا","display":"خَطَاً"},{"kind":"word","token":"فعليه","display":"فَعَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"عتق","display":"عِتْقُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"رقبه","display":"رَقَبَةٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"مؤمنه","display":"مُؤْمِنَةٍ"},{"kind":"word","token":"او","display":"اَوْ"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"word","token":"فصيام","display":"فَصِيٰامُ"},{"kind":"word","token":"شهرين","display":"شَهْرَيْنِ"},{"kind":"word","token":"متتابعين","display":"مُتَتٰابِعَيْنِ"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"quranic_text"},{"kind":"tag_open","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"المجادله","display":"المجادلة"},{"kind":"word","token":"۴","display":"۴"},{"kind":"tag_close","tag_name":"footnote"},{"kind":"word","token":"او","display":"اَوْ"